      <ContentCard
        slug="/blog/llm-experience"
        title="LLM Experience: The Missing Discipline in AI Development"
        description="While prompts and tools get attention, the biggest opportunity in AI development lies in designing information architecture that optimizes for AI cognition. LLM Experience is the discipline that changes AI systems from functional to exceptional."
